(16, 1, '2024-12-30 16:34:59', '2024-12-30 16:34:59', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Position:</strong> Marketing Manager<br><strong>Location:</strong> New York, NY (Hybrid options available)<br><strong>Department:</strong> Marketing<br><strong>Job Type:</strong> Full-Time</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Are you a creative and strategic thinker with a passion for digital marketing? Do you have a track record of driving brand growth and delivering successful campaigns? Were looking for a talented <strong>Marketing Manager</strong> to join our growing team at <strong>Bright Horizon Solutions</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a Marketing Manager, youll be responsible for leading our marketing initiatives, developing and executing campaigns, and driving our brands growth across multiple channels. If you\'re excited to be part of a dynamic team, we want to hear from you!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Develop, implement, and manage multi-channel marketing campaigns.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Analyze market trends and customer insights to optimize campaigns.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Oversee social media strategy and content creation for the brand.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Collaborate with cross-functional teams to ensure brand consistency.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Manage marketing budget and track ROI on all campaigns.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Lead and mentor junior marketing team members.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Bachelors degree in Marketing, Business, or a related field.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Minimum of 5 years of experience in digital marketing or brand management.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Proven experience in campaign management, social media, and content marketing.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Strong communication, leadership, and project management skills.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Proficiency in Google Analytics, SEO, SEM, and email marketing platforms.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Ability to work in a fast-paced, dynamic environment.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>What We Offer:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Competitive salary ($70,000 - $90,000/year).</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Health, dental, and vision insurance.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>401(k) with company match.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Flexible working hours and remote work options.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Professional development and career growth opportunities.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>A fun, inclusive, and creative company culture.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>How to Apply:</strong> If you\'re ready to take your career to the next level, please submit your resume and a cover letter to <strong><a>careers@brighthorizon.com</a></strong> by <strong>January 15, 2024</strong>. In your cover letter, tell us why youre excited about this opportunity and how your experience aligns with the role.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Application Deadline:</strong> January 15, 2024</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>At <strong>Bright Horizon Solutions</strong>, we are an equal opportunity employer. We embrace diversity and are committed to creating an inclusive environment for all employees.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'We\'re Hiring! Join Our Marketing Team!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1-revision-v1', '', '', '2024-12-30 16:34:59', '2024-12-30 16:34:59', '', 1, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=16', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
